Text: MFS Municipal Income Trust (MFM) to Issue  -  Dividend of $0.03 on September 30th . Investors of record on Wednesday, September 18th will be given a dividend of 0.027 per share by the closed-end fund on Monday, September 30th. This represents a yield of 4.8%.
